    excerpt: 'Workplace bullying and harassment are more common than many people realise, and young adults in their first jobs are particularly vulnerable. Knowing your rights and how to respond can make a real difference.',
    metaDescription: 'A guide for young adults on recognising workplace bullying and harassment, understanding your rights, how to report it, and protecting your mental health when work becomes hostile.',
